title: Suspension
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The //suspension// of a topological space $$X$$ is the quotient space $$\sigma X \coloneqq X \times I/\!\sim$$ where $$(x,0) \sim (y,0)$$ and $$(x,1) \sim (y,1)$$ for all $$x,y \in X.$$